@startuml
title Weather Station System State Transition Diagram

initial : [Initial]
state Running {
    state ConfigMode
    state Shutdown
    state ControlledMode
}

initial --> Running : Restart and Begin Running

Running --> ConfigMode : Changes or Power-saving Settings Required
ConfigMode --> Running : Configuration Completed

Running --> Running : Data Collection (Clock Triggered)
Running --> SummaryMode : Prepare and Send Out Weather Summary
SummaryMode --> Running : Return to Running State

Running --> StatusCheckMode : Check Own Status
StatusCheckMode --> Running : Return to Running State

Running --> ControlledMode : Remote Control
ControlledMode --> Shutdown : Shutdown Command Given

Shutdown --> Running : Shutdown Command Given (Reverse Transition)

@enduml
